  "name": "Crippling Thrust",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/yellow_03.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>With one precise stab, you hamper movement.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Weapon Focus with piercing weapon, base attack bonus +6.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As a standard action, make a single attack with your chosen weapon. If the attack hits, the target's movement speed is halved until the start of your next turn. When your base attack bonus reaches +11, the target's movement is so hampered that even a 5-foot step provokes an attack of opportunity. When your base attack bonus reaches +16, the target must also succeed at a Reflex save with a DC equal to 10 + your base attack bonus or become entangled. An entangled creature's movement can be halved only once. You can use this feat's benefits only once per minute.",
